                            <strong>Cloud TTS Providers:</strong> Your text (or text chunks) and your API key are sent directly to the provider you select (Google, ElevenLabs, etc.) over HTTPS.
                        </MudListItem>
                        <MudListItem T="string" Icon="@Icons.Material.Filled.Block">
                            <strong>What's NOT sent:</strong> Your master password, your file contents before synthesis, your settings, your usage history, or any identifying information beyond what the TTS API requires.
                        </MudListItem>
                    </MudList>

                    <MudText Typo="Typo.body2" Class="mt-3" Color="Color.Secondary">
